Class::Accessor::Lite
===========================

Class::Accessor::Lite is a minimalitsic variant of Class::Accessor.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

See Makefile.PL.

